pure function:
    does not depends on value outside the function
    no side effects


immutability:
    FP (functional programming) emphasize on the concept of immutability


recursive:
    FP also emphasize on recursive


higher-order function:
    a function that can receive other function as its arguments, returns a function, or both
    JS has first-class function ability, thus able to do above


reusable function:
    function that is reusable because it is a pure function

        Array.map()
        Array.filter()
        Array.reduce()  
        Array.every()
        Array.some()
        Array.find()
        Array.sort()
        Array.forEach()